00:13:48.870 --> 00:13:50.787
You could do some live
stuff on the device

00:13:50.787 --> 00:13:52.120
with the new version of Android.

00:13:52.120 --> 00:13:54.760
And screen share, you can
do some stuff with that.

00:13:54.760 --> 00:13:57.100
But you do have to be
aware that it's obviously

00:13:57.100 --> 00:14:00.960
pretty-- encoding a video can
be kind of hard and on a phone,

00:14:00.960 --> 00:14:03.422
